HEADWORD: Libelant
<hw>Li"bel*ant</hw> <pr>(-⟦ait⟧nt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
libels; one who institutes a suit in an ecclesiastical or admiralty
court.</def> <altsp>[Written also <asp>libellant</asp>.]</altsp>
<rj><au>Cranch.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
